Armed men suspected to be bandits have invaded the Federal Government College, Birnin Yauri, Kebbis State and abducted a yet to be specified number of female students. Details of the incident are still sketchy but according to Daily Trust, there are reports that a security operative was shot dead during the operation. The state’s Public Relations Officer, DSP Nafiu Abubakar was unable to take his calls and could not respond to text message forwarded to him as at press time. More to follow….